Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:25.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}当她仰起头时 我可以看到她的脑子{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm telling you,she leaned back,I could see her brain.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:28.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你到底要拒绝多少好女孩…{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}How many women will you reject...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:31.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}只是因为非常肤浅的事情？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}...over superficial,insignificant things{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:34.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}慢着，我必须帮钱德说话{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Hold it. I gotta side with Chandler on this one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:37.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我刚搬到这里时 与一个女孩交往{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}When I first moved here,I went out with this girl.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:39.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}非常热情，很会接吻…{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Really hot. Great kisser...{\r}
