Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:49.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你说还是我说？ 我来好了{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-You or me? -I got it.{\r}
