Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:08.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}因为她不讨厌音乐家雅尼 这不是个正当的理由{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Because she doesn't hate Yanni is not a real reason.{\r}
