Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:31.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我们会小声一点{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}We'll try to keep it down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:33.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:36.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我要回去继续我的晚宴了{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm going to rejoin my dinner party.{\r}
