Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}对了，珍妮丝{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Okay,Janice.{\r}
