Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:42.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}怎么发生的？ 他大概在扫地{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-How did this happen? -He was sweeping.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:44.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}他们发现他抓着一把扫把{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}They found a broom in his hand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}真糟糕 我知道{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-That's terrible. -I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}昨天我也在扫地{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I was sweeping yesterday.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:53.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}搞不好也会一命呜呼{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}It could've been me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}扫地，真是没想到{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Sweeping. You never know.{\r}
