Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:07.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}很微弱 但我还可以感觉他在大楼里{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}It's very faint,but I can still sense him in the building.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:11.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}进入光芒中，哈克先生！{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Go into the light,Mr. Heckles!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}好了，菲比{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Okay,Phoebe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}对不起 有时候他们需要帮助{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm sorry,but sometimes they need help.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:22.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}又来了{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Here we go.{\r}
