Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:27.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我不相信很多事情…{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}There are a lot of things I don't believe in...{\r}
