Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:31.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}譬如什么事？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Such as?{\r}
