Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:48.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你不相信进化论？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}You don't believe in evolution?{\r}
