Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:55.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}猴子，达尔文，很好的故事 我只是觉得有点太简单{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Monkeys,Darwin,it's a nice story. I just think it's a little too easy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:01.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}太简单？太…{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}"Too easy"? Too{\r}
